      "repair_reason": "Protected maintainer label plus a user-facing config/tool-scope change and insufficient custom/LanceDB live proof make this a human-review item, not an automated repair.; Cleared: No concrete supply-chain regression found; the tool-scope expansion is exact-config controlled and filters wildcard, group, and local core tool names. (sha=bd52e995de05e17964b1eb23f1375a3466de64ca)",
